      <arrangement id="aspace_b3a418765619f31a34e92f5af3d185b9">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged in two series: I. Images: prints, negatives, and slides, circa 1952-circa 1979.  II. Interviews conducted for <title>
               <part>Saarinen's Quest: A Memoir</part>
            </title>, 2001-2003.</p>  
      </arrangement>
